  "detailed_description": "The demo of the Wilson game update has been released. Wilson is a game like 2D Resident Evil. It also tells the adventures of a rabbit named Nurtopu. The aim is to collect diamonds and magic tubes, take them to the desired location and win the boss battles. It is a 2D platform game. The game is simple to play. My aim while making this game was to ensure that the player has a stress-free time. When we look at it from this perspective, we can call it a \"hyper casual 2D platform game\".<br>There is also a Wilson demo update in the game. It is like a 2D version of Wilson Resident Evil. We can say that it is a local and national Resident Evil.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570950/extras/57f29007bedc0cd5c5e0f00b246b2e4f.poster.avif?t=1720130681\" width=256 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570950/extras/57f29007bedc0cd5c5e0f00b246b2e4f.webm?t=1720130681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570950/extras/57f29007bedc0cd5c5e0f00b246b2e4f.mp4?t=1720130681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
